ANDS-Grants.description: This project examines the conversion of farmland for development in China, and examines how different modes of land conversion affect people's participation in local governance, community cohesion and conflict. The research will enhance understanding of domestic Chinese political processes.
ANDS-Grants.title: Converting farmland for development: politics, community and conflict in China
